WEBVTT

00:00:16.160 --> 00:00:17.879
It doesn't make sense.

00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:19.920
That fake husband of yours

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:21.960
is just an ordinary food delivery guy.

00:00:22.239 --> 00:00:24.079
Mr. Zhou from Tiange Group

00:00:24.079 --> 00:00:26.320
Why would he appreciate him so much?

00:00:26.519 --> 00:00:27.960
I just can't figure it out.

00:00:28.199 --> 00:00:29.120
It's really baffling.

00:00:29.719 --> 00:00:31.320
None of this makes any sense.

00:00:31.320 --> 00:00:32.880
We're talking about a hundred million here.

00:00:34.759 --> 00:00:35.799
I just don't believe it.

00:00:36.079 --> 00:00:37.759
Just because they hit it off at first meeting

00:00:37.759 --> 00:00:39.320
he'd give him so much money?

00:00:39.399 --> 00:00:40.719
Unless this Mr. Zhou

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:43.159
has some special fetish.

00:00:45.560 --> 00:00:47.439
Gao Xing is secretly having an affair with him.

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:49.840
Don't talk nonsense.

00:00:50.240 --> 00:00:52.560
Gao Xing is a normal man.

00:00:54.079 --> 00:00:55.439
How do you know that?

00:00:56.039 --> 00:00:56.399
You—

00:00:56.399 --> 00:00:57.679
Have you tried?

00:00:59.280 --> 00:01:00.119
No, I haven't.

00:01:00.119 --> 00:01:01.280
Of course I haven't.

00:01:02.079 --> 00:01:03.039
Qingyan.

00:01:03.960 --> 00:01:05.280
You're acting strange.

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:06.879
You're blushing.

00:01:07.920 --> 00:01:09.480
Oh, stop teasing me.

00:01:09.480 --> 00:01:10.400
Be serious.

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:11.799
Come on, tell the truth.

00:01:11.799 --> 00:01:13.000
I know you too well.

00:01:13.159 --> 00:01:15.319
Did you and he already do something?

00:01:15.319 --> 00:01:17.200
No, really, we didn't.

00:01:18.680 --> 00:01:20.439
I just—

00:01:20.439 --> 00:01:21.280
Just what?

00:01:21.280 --> 00:01:22.159
Hurry, tell me.

00:01:24.079 --> 00:01:25.239
It's just that day—

00:01:25.239 --> 00:01:26.599
He helped me solve a big problem.

00:01:26.599 --> 00:01:27.599
I was so happy at the time.

00:01:27.599 --> 00:01:28.959
So I invited Gao Xing out for drinks.

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:30.200
Then I drank too much and I—

00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:32.920
Just—

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:34.959
I just—

00:01:35.079 --> 00:01:36.719
I took the initiative and kissed him.

00:01:36.879 --> 00:01:38.480
It was just a kiss.

00:01:38.560 --> 00:01:40.359
Did anything else happen?

00:01:40.359 --> 00:01:41.159
Of course not.

00:01:43.480 --> 00:01:45.400
Everyone was drunk.

00:01:45.480 --> 00:01:47.079
They even took the initiative to kiss.

00:01:47.480 --> 00:01:49.799
But nothing else happened.

00:01:50.079 --> 00:01:51.200
Is he even a man?

00:01:51.359 --> 00:01:53.200
Now I'm even more suspicious of Gao Xing.

00:01:53.200 --> 00:01:54.640
Something's not right between him and President Zhou.

00:01:54.799 --> 00:01:55.920
Don't talk nonsense.

00:01:56.640 --> 00:01:59.159
Gao Xing may seem unreliable,

00:01:59.239 --> 00:02:00.879
but he's actually a good person.

00:02:01.319 --> 00:02:03.560
Now you're even defending him.

00:02:04.480 --> 00:02:07.760
Are you two actually getting together for real?

00:02:07.760 --> 00:02:08.680
How could that be?

00:02:09.599 --> 00:02:11.960
He and I are just business partners.

00:02:12.080 --> 00:02:13.680
I'm not interested in him at all.

00:02:17.719 --> 00:02:19.240
Alright, that's enough.

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:20.800
Let's get back to business.

00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:23.400
Previously, it was because of funding issues

00:02:23.400 --> 00:02:24.800
that our new product, Royal Beauty Cream,

00:02:24.800 --> 00:02:26.199
couldn't go into production.

00:02:26.800 --> 00:02:28.599
Now that the money problem is solved,

00:02:28.879 --> 00:02:30.439
let's hurry and start production.

00:02:30.439 --> 00:02:32.159
Don't worry, leave it to me.

00:02:32.159 --> 00:02:33.280
Within seven days,

00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:35.439
our first batch of new products will definitely hit the market.

00:02:35.439 --> 00:02:36.439
I guarantee they'll sell like crazy.

00:02:36.680 --> 00:02:38.599
By then, our Qingmu Technology

00:02:38.599 --> 00:02:40.360
will really take off.

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:44.199
How could this happen?

00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:46.080
Why is this happening?

00:02:47.800 --> 00:02:48.680
Young Master Song,

00:02:48.879 --> 00:02:50.479
Could that guy really be Gao Feng?

00:02:51.199 --> 00:02:53.240
Otherwise, even President Zhou from Tiange Group

00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:55.479
wouldn't be so polite to him.

00:02:56.879 --> 00:02:57.960
Can't you understand what I'm saying?

00:02:58.080 --> 00:02:58.919
I've already told you,

00:02:58.919 --> 00:03:00.599
Zhou Pengfei told me himself.

00:03:00.639 --> 00:03:01.879
He's investing in Qingmu Group,

00:03:01.879 --> 00:03:03.680
and it has nothing to do with whether he's Gao Feng or not.

00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:05.599
But that's a hundred million!

00:03:05.800 --> 00:03:07.479
Then why do you think President Zhou

00:03:07.479 --> 00:03:09.000
is so eager to give him money?

00:03:09.159 --> 00:03:10.879
How should I know what kind of crazy idea Zhou has?

00:03:12.919 --> 00:03:14.319
So what do we do now?

00:03:14.599 --> 00:03:17.199
I can't lose my position as Qingmu's deputy general manager.

00:03:18.039 --> 00:03:21.120
Su Qingyan thinks that with the formula and funding,

00:03:21.560 --> 00:03:22.960
she can completely turn things around.

00:03:24.520 --> 00:03:25.919
But what if,

00:03:26.319 --> 00:03:29.479
her formula suddenly became useless?

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:32.080
What would happen then?

00:03:32.800 --> 00:03:33.599
Useless?

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:36.159
What do you mean?

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:38.120
What I mean is,

00:03:40.479 --> 00:03:41.280
for this matter,

00:03:43.159 --> 00:03:44.800
President Su, it still has to be you

00:03:45.439 --> 00:03:46.599
who handles it personally.

00:03:46.599 --> 00:03:47.560
Me?

00:03:51.919 --> 00:03:52.759
How could I do that?

00:03:52.879 --> 00:03:54.080
That's a crime!

00:03:57.280 --> 00:04:00.240
You'll get half of the money we make.

00:04:06.639 --> 00:04:07.240
Alright.

00:04:11.159 --> 00:04:14.039
Then, Young Master Song, let's have a pleasant cooperation.

00:04:23.279 --> 00:04:24.079
Qingyan

00:04:24.879 --> 00:04:25.560
Qingyan

00:04:25.800 --> 00:04:26.399
Something's wrong.

00:04:26.639 --> 00:04:28.639
Song Group just announced the launch of a new product.

00:04:28.680 --> 00:04:30.079
They're producing our Royal Beauty Cream.

00:04:30.879 --> 00:04:31.680
Royal Beauty Cream?

00:04:33.399 --> 00:04:35.839
Isn't Royal Beauty Cream our exclusive Qingmu formula?

00:04:36.040 --> 00:04:36.879
Are you sure you didn't make a mistake?

00:04:36.879 --> 00:04:38.199
I've double-checked it many times.

00:04:38.199 --> 00:04:39.040
It's definitely Royal Beauty Cream.

00:04:39.040 --> 00:04:40.360
This can't be a coincidence.

00:04:41.120 --> 00:04:42.639
You mean...

00:04:42.639 --> 00:04:44.879
Song Group stole our formula.

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:46.480
That's right.

00:04:47.040 --> 00:04:48.959
Royal Beauty Cream is Qingmu's top secret.

00:04:49.160 --> 00:04:51.399
Only four people in the whole company have access to the formula.

00:04:51.399 --> 00:04:52.720
Besides you and me,

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:54.279
there's Chief Consultant Zhou from R&amp;D,

00:04:54.480 --> 00:04:55.720
and the only one left is

00:04:56.319 --> 00:04:57.399
Su Zhengdong.

00:05:02.600 --> 00:05:03.680
Hello?

00:05:08.680 --> 00:05:09.480
What is it?

00:05:10.879 --> 00:05:11.879
Song Haoyang is here.

00:05:22.519 --> 00:05:23.360
That Song guy...

00:05:23.439 --> 00:05:24.639
You stole our Royal Beauty formula,

00:05:24.639 --> 00:05:25.639
and you still have the nerve to show up.

00:05:28.439 --> 00:05:31.639
The formula was developed independently by our Song Group.

00:05:32.079 --> 00:05:33.600
Don't make false accusations.

00:05:33.959 --> 00:05:35.000
Besides,

00:05:35.560 --> 00:05:36.800
our rejuvenating cream

00:05:36.920 --> 00:05:39.879
was launched earlier than your Qingmu's.

00:05:40.199 --> 00:05:42.240
If Qingmu's beauty cream

00:05:42.360 --> 00:05:43.680
is the same as ours,

00:05:44.199 --> 00:05:47.600
then the real thief is you, isn't it?

00:05:47.959 --> 00:05:49.639
You're still twisting the truth.

00:05:49.720 --> 00:05:52.199
You clearly instigated Su Zhengdong to steal this formula.

00:05:52.759 --> 00:05:53.560
Uncle Si,

00:05:54.079 --> 00:05:55.680
as the vice president of Qingmu,

00:05:56.079 --> 00:05:57.360
for your own personal gain,

00:05:57.360 --> 00:05:59.199
you betrayed the company and colluded with Song Group.

00:05:59.399 --> 00:06:00.879
Do you have any sense of shame left?

00:06:01.439 --> 00:06:02.360
Qingyan,

00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:04.079
you can eat whatever you want,

00:06:04.199 --> 00:06:05.800
but you can't say whatever you want.

00:06:06.279 --> 00:06:08.639
I, Su Zhengdong, have always acted with integrity.

00:06:09.560 --> 00:06:11.279
You accuse me of selling the formula,

00:06:11.279 --> 00:06:12.800
you say I betrayed the company,

00:06:12.839 --> 00:06:14.240
but you need evidence for that.

00:06:14.759 --> 00:06:15.600
Otherwise,

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:16.879
I can sue you for slander.

00:06:16.879 --> 00:06:17.399
You...

00:06:18.120 --> 00:06:18.399
You...

00:06:18.399 --> 00:06:19.600
You are utterly shameless!

00:06:20.040 --> 00:06:21.279
Business is like a battlefield.

00:06:21.959 --> 00:06:23.600
What's wrong with using a few tricks?

00:06:23.959 --> 00:06:26.600
Anyway, we've already launched our rejuvenating cream.

00:06:28.879 --> 00:06:29.759
Right now,

00:06:30.680 --> 00:06:34.360
your Qingmu's formula is nothing but a worthless piece of paper.

00:06:34.879 --> 00:06:35.720
Qingyan,

00:06:35.879 --> 00:06:38.439
I told you, you can't beat me.

00:06:39.439 --> 00:06:41.199
But as long as you change your mind

00:06:41.360 --> 00:06:43.519
and obediently divorce that Gao and marry me,

00:06:44.079 --> 00:06:45.560
I might consider

00:06:45.800 --> 00:06:48.160
letting your Qingmu produce the same Royal Beauty Cream.

00:06:48.879 --> 00:06:50.160
After all,

00:06:50.360 --> 00:06:52.959
when a couple works together, nothing is impossible.

00:06:54.800 --> 00:06:56.480
This Royal Beauty Cream was ours to begin with.

00:06:56.759 --> 00:06:58.600
You're using our own product to make a deal with us.

00:06:58.600 --> 00:06:59.720
Do you have any shame at all?

00:07:00.959 --> 00:07:02.079
Say whatever you want.

00:07:02.680 --> 00:07:03.680
I know

00:07:03.920 --> 00:07:05.480
that to produce the Royal Beauty Cream,

00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:07.680
you've already invested a huge amount of money.

00:07:08.199 --> 00:07:10.199
If all that money goes down the drain,

00:07:10.399 --> 00:07:12.000
the consequences will be unimaginable.

00:07:12.879 --> 00:07:13.680
Qingyan,

00:07:14.600 --> 00:07:18.560
Qingmu's fate is entirely in your hands.

00:07:20.560 --> 00:07:22.480
I, Su Qingyan, never accept threats.

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:24.680
So what if the formula was stolen?

00:07:25.120 --> 00:07:27.040
Qingmu still has funds in the account.

00:07:27.480 --> 00:07:28.720
At worst, I'll pay a high price

00:07:28.720 --> 00:07:30.680
to buy a new secret formula and start production again.

00:07:30.680 --> 00:07:31.480
By then,

00:07:31.720 --> 00:07:34.639
I'll be able to defeat your Song Group fair and square.

00:07:37.480 --> 00:07:38.279
Hmm.

00:07:39.560 --> 00:07:40.639
That's really impressive.

00:07:42.199 --> 00:07:45.240
No wonder you're the woman who founded Qingmu herself.

00:07:46.439 --> 00:07:47.560
But it's a pity,

00:07:47.839 --> 00:07:49.480
even if you buy a new formula,

00:07:50.199 --> 00:07:52.399
it will all be in vain.

00:07:56.800 --> 00:07:58.639
President Zhao, come in.

00:08:03.879 --> 00:08:04.959
Who is this person?

00:08:05.639 --> 00:08:06.399
President Zhao.

00:08:06.639 --> 00:08:07.040
You...

00:08:07.279 --> 00:08:08.800
You are Zhao Xinglin.

00:08:08.959 --> 00:08:09.759
Master Zhao.

00:08:10.759 --> 00:08:13.079
I didn't expect such a small company

00:08:13.079 --> 00:08:15.439
would have someone who recognizes me.

00:08:15.720 --> 00:08:17.439
You have a sharp eye.

00:08:17.879 --> 00:08:19.800
Mr. Zhou, who is this person?

00:08:19.800 --> 00:08:20.600
President Su.

00:08:21.120 --> 00:08:24.800
This is the president of the Southern Province Pharmacists Association.

00:08:25.000 --> 00:08:25.959
His medical skills are extraordinary.

00:08:26.160 --> 00:08:27.879
He is considered the best in Yun City.

00:08:27.879 --> 00:08:30.879
That Master Chen we previously sought for a formula

00:08:31.360 --> 00:08:32.799
is actually his disciple.

00:08:33.279 --> 00:08:34.080
That's right.

00:08:34.440 --> 00:08:37.559
President Zhao is not only the president of the Southern Province Pharmacists Association,

00:08:37.840 --> 00:08:40.440
but also a disciple of the legendary Ancient Medical Family.

00:08:40.960 --> 00:08:44.480
It's because my Song family has a close relationship with President Zhao

00:08:45.080 --> 00:08:47.279
that we were able to invite him here.

00:08:47.399 --> 00:08:48.840
Young Master Song, you flatter me.

00:08:50.080 --> 00:08:51.799
I was just fortunate

00:08:51.799 --> 00:08:55.080
to become a registered disciple of the Ancient Medical Family.

00:08:55.360 --> 00:08:59.559
This is also the proudest achievement of my life.

00:09:00.200 --> 00:09:03.279
The Ancient Medical Family is a sacred place for medicine in our country.

00:09:03.399 --> 00:09:06.200
As a registered disciple of the Ancient Medical Family,

00:09:06.399 --> 00:09:08.879
President Zhao's medical skills are unmatched in Yun City.

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:11.000
Watch closely.

00:09:11.679 --> 00:09:13.679
This is the new formula he prepared for our Song Group—

00:09:13.679 --> 00:09:16.399
the Rejuvenating Cream.

00:09:24.799 --> 00:09:25.879
The formula is exquisite.

00:09:26.080 --> 00:09:28.039
Truly the work of a master.

00:09:28.480 --> 00:09:31.639
This rejuvenating cream is made from eight precious medicinal ingredients.

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:33.440
It can remove spots and whiten the skin.

00:09:33.759 --> 00:09:36.039
It keeps the skin smooth and radiant for a long time.

00:09:36.559 --> 00:09:37.600
With long-term use,

00:09:37.960 --> 00:09:41.080
it can greatly slow down the aging process in women.

00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:44.600
Its effects are ten times better than Qingmu’s beauty cream.

00:09:44.600 --> 00:09:46.080
Ten times stronger!

00:09:48.799 --> 00:09:51.039
Even if Qingmu spends money to buy a new formula,

00:09:51.039 --> 00:09:53.279
at best, it would only reach the level of Chen Daoyuan.

00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:56.240
President Zhao is actually Chen Daoyuan’s master.

00:09:56.399 --> 00:09:58.840
His medical skills are ten times better than his.

00:09:59.879 --> 00:10:04.360
So what does Qingmu have to compete with me?

00:10:05.399 --> 00:10:06.200
Qingyan,

00:10:06.639 --> 00:10:07.559
what should we do now?

00:10:10.279 --> 00:10:10.960
Elder Zhou,

00:10:10.960 --> 00:10:13.000
If President Zhao’s formula is second best,

00:10:13.240 --> 00:10:16.080
no one in the southern province would dare claim to be first.

00:10:16.440 --> 00:10:18.799
The formulas Qingmu could buy before

00:10:18.799 --> 00:10:20.399
can’t compare to this rejuvenating cream.

00:10:20.600 --> 00:10:22.159
A formula of this level

00:10:22.600 --> 00:10:25.360
can’t be bought with money anymore.

00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:28.159
That’s right.

00:10:28.159 --> 00:10:29.279
That Chen Daoyuan kid

00:10:29.399 --> 00:10:32.639
was just my most disappointing disciple.

00:10:33.080 --> 00:10:36.080
Looking across Yun City and the entire southern province,

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:37.799
except for the ancient medical families,

00:10:38.039 --> 00:10:39.960
anyone else’s secret formulas

00:10:40.080 --> 00:10:41.639
in my eyes,

00:10:41.799 --> 00:10:44.120
are nothing but worthless paper.

00:10:49.279 --> 00:10:50.960
Other people’s secret formulas are worthless paper?

00:10:52.600 --> 00:10:53.639
What about yours?

00:10:54.519 --> 00:10:56.759
Your secret formula is also worthless paper in my eyes.